message.content: Minions dog, Rang! the Rev. Edwards, who hadn't enjoyed himself so much since reading Treasure Island. "What have you got in that barrel, Price?", he roared. Quelled, Mr. Price pulled out a grocery list, pushed his glasses up on his nose, and began to read. "Six loaves, four pounds butter, two pounds marge, one tin pineapple, one loaf ham."
